title: DC SHOES: MALCOLM STEWART - THE CONTENDER
description:
Check out DC motocross athlete Malcolm Stewart testing his KTM 250SX-F at the KTM test track in Corona, CA last week. Malcolm's getting ready to race for the 2012 East Coast Lites Championships. The nine race series kicks off in Dallas, Texas on Saturday, February 18th. 

Follow the DC Moto team:
